data.description: Welcome to Los Lagos! This custom Tudor estate built in 1991 boasts over 5500 square feet of living area and overlooks the breathtaking pond and greenbelt. When you walk into this lovely home, you will be amazed by the craftsmanship that went into the construction of this unique property. The kitchen possesses beautiful granite counter tops and top of the line stainless steel appliances, including 4 ovens, 2 dishwashers and an enormous Viking refrigerator. Love to entertain? Then put on some music through the surround sound, turn on any of the 4 fire places throughout the home, or relax in the backyard by the pool and enjoy time with friends and family. After you are all done with entertaining, you can head up and relax in the master suite fit for royalty. All of this with owned solar? Your dream home awaits...
